this, having been given the chance to be restored, she was not going to allow 
herself to be deactivated again. She turned around & ran. Then transformed in 
mid stride to flee the group, leaping into the shadows & escaping. She would 
convince Alpha Trion to assist her. Only he & Vector Sigma could help her. As 
much as she hated to admit it. 


